  "detailed_description": "<h1>Keep Games</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Topac Battles</strong>, an idle game like no other, where magical and cozy monsters await your discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/410914bd7c9ef7ffe486894fe4bf84c5.poster.avif?t=1728991620\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/410914bd7c9ef7ffe486894fe4bf84c5.webm?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 18 Monsters across 7 rarities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed and evolve Monsters up to Gen 3!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn money through Monster battles or sales!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase 3 new Topac type with your earnings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Access 4 unique Topac, each offering different rarities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your battle lineup to 6 hexagons!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push your limits with unlimited battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your park's capacity to 100!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture increasingly rare Monsters after battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Name your Monsters and park!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters hunt and feed while offline; return to see their progress!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy more parks and switch between them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create a feeding frenzy to grow your Monster!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/3749123ba0953cc997c5198c94575830.poster.avif?t=1728991620\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/3749123ba0953cc997c5198c94575830.webm?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/3749123ba0953cc997c5198c94575830.mp4?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock rare Monsters through with Topacs!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/31b38eef89d589841daa62c572f59a82.poster.avif?t=1728991620\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/31b38eef89d589841daa62c572f59a82.webm?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/31b38eef89d589841daa62c572f59a82.mp4?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"With 18 Topac Monsters currently in the game and plans to introduce more Monster species and forms, we foresee the need for a larger team and more time. Through Early Access, with your help, we aim to gather ideas for different races and Topac Monters varieties, gradually increasing Topac diversity with incremental upgrades.\"</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Topac Battles</strong>, an idle game like no other, where magical and cozy monsters await your discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/410914bd7c9ef7ffe486894fe4bf84c5.poster.avif?t=1728991620\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/410914bd7c9ef7ffe486894fe4bf84c5.webm?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 18 Monsters across 7 rarities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed and evolve Monsters up to Gen 3!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn money through Monster battles or sales!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase 3 new Topac type with your earnings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Access 4 unique Topac, each offering different rarities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your battle lineup to 6 hexagons!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push your limits with unlimited battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your park's capacity to 100!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture increasingly rare Monsters after battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Name your Monsters and park!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters hunt and feed while offline; return to see their progress!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy more parks and switch between them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create a feeding frenzy to grow your Monster!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/3749123ba0953cc997c5198c94575830.poster.avif?t=1728991620\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/3749123ba0953cc997c5198c94575830.webm?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/3749123ba0953cc997c5198c94575830.mp4?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock rare Monsters through with Topacs!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/31b38eef89d589841daa62c572f59a82.poster.avif?t=1728991620\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/31b38eef89d589841daa62c572f59a82.webm?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/31b38eef89d589841daa62c572f59a82.mp4?t=1728991620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"With 18 Topac Monsters currently in the game and plans to introduce more Monster species and forms, we foresee the need for a larger team and more time. Through Early Access, with your help, we aim to gather ideas for different races and Topac Monters varieties, gradually increasing Topac diversity with incremental upgrades.\"</p>",
